race.comment: ROMA GREEN (2) Snitzel gelding from Showbeel on debut for the Baker stable. The stable have had great success kicking them off in the bush, and the two latest trials have been solid. Go close. CAMILLA (4) made it four minor placings in a row last start when a fighting second over 1300m at Canberra. Finds a suitable contest and no excuses from the inside gate. AEROSTERN BRO (1) Astern gelding resuming after improving at each run in his first campaign. Kept finding with the 59kg when second over 1400m here on the heavy track last May. Two trials had merit and shapes as a leading player. BEDDA MIA (6) strong through the line when an improved third over 1000m at Canberra. Gets map favours and should appreciate the extra trip.
